  <name>Tikra</name>
  <summary>A simple clock application for AetherDE</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Tikra is a simple and elegant clock application designed for the AetherDE desktop environment.
      It displays the current time and date in a clean, easy-to-read interface that follows GNOME Human Interface Guidelines.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time clock display with seconds precision</li>
      <li>Current date display</li>
      <li>Clean and minimalist design</li>
      <li>Follows GNOME HIG design patterns</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">org.aether.tikra.desktop</launchable>
